    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Mokuton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 10 (Spell Level 5)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 25 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 13 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 27</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>The target area must have bushes and trees for this technique to be effective. You send your Chakra into the area, causing living plants to grow wildly and out of control. The area becomes equivalent to a thicket or jungle, allowing creatures to move through it at only 5 ft per round (or 10 ft for Large or larger creatures).</p>\n\n\n\n",
